sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant RCV as Recovery MW
    participant RID as RequestID MW
    participant LOG as Logger MW
    participant RL as RateLimit MW
    participant CORS as CORS MW
    participant AUTH as Auth MW
    participant TR as TenantResolver MW
    participant RBAC as RBAC MW
    participant H as Handler
    participant SVC as Service
    participant QR as QueryRegistry
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    C->>RCV: HTTP request
    RCV->>RID: (panic guard active)
    RID->>LOG: set X-Request-ID on context
    LOG->>RL: record start time
    RL->>CORS: check per-IP token bucket
    alt rate limit exceeded
        CORS-->>C: 429 Too Many Requests
    end
    CORS->>AUTH: handle OPTIONS or append CORS headers
    AUTH->>TR: parse + validate JWT
    alt invalid or missing JWT
        TR-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
    end
    TR->>RBAC: set orgID on context
    RBAC->>H: check role vs required permission
    alt permission denied
        H-->>C: 403 Forbidden + audit event written
    end
    H->>SVC: call service function
    SVC->>QR: QueryRegistry.Get("group.name")
    QR->>PG: execute prepared statement (org-scoped)
    PG-->>QR: result rows
    QR-->>SVC: rows
    SVC-->>H: domain types
    H-->>LOG: encode JSON response
    LOG-->>C: HTTP response + log latency
